MiniMailer.mcc/MUIA_MiniMailer_TranslateHook

    NAME
     MUIA_MiniMailer_TranslateHook (v16) -- struct Hook, [ISG.] 


    FUNCTION
     You may define a hook to translate the text string to your
     codeset or just set the codeset name.
     
     The hook is called as:
     
     struct Hook *hook,struct MUIS_MiniMailer_Translate *tra
     a0                a2

     where tra fields are: 
    
     text - the text to be translated
     codesetName - write here your codeset name
     codesetNameLen - codesetName buffer length
     flags - leave 0 for now
     
     The hook must return the translated string (it is ok to
     return tra->text itself).
     
