MiniMailer.mcc/MUIM_MiniMailer_Translate

    NAME
     MUIM_MiniMailer_Translate (v16)


    SYNOPSIS
     STRPTR res = DoMethod(obj,MUIM_MiniMailer_Translate,STRPTR text,STRPTR codesetName,
                               ULONG codesetNameLen,ULONG flags)


    FUNCTION
     This is called on object when it is needed to translate a
     string.

     text - the text to be translated
     codesetName - write here your codeset name
     codesetNameLen - codesetName buffer length
     flags - always 0 for now
     
